                <entry>10.5.1</entry>
                <entry>Investigate average rate of change between two independent values of a function.</entry>
                <entry>The central aspect of rate of change to differential calculus is a basis to further understanding of limits, gradients and calculations and formulae necessary for work in engineering fields, e.g. designing roads, bridges etc. </entry>
